premise_source_doc_sentence: Bhool Bhulaiyaa  (  English : The Maze  )  is a 2007 Indian drama/comedy horror film directed by Priyadarshan .
It constitutes the official remake of the 1993 Malayalam film , Manichitrathazhu , starring Mohanlal .
which was already remade into several Indian films .
